name: FALL INTO PURPLE
description:
Kesedihan. Ekspresi diri yang dapat dinikmati secara eksklusif dan sangat personal. Jatuh di dalam kesedihan, membawa pada momentum bangkit kembali. Selamat merayakan kesedihan.

Sadness. Self-expression that can be enjoyed in an exclusive and very personal way. Falling in sorrow brings on momentum to rise again. Happy celebrating sadness.
